Best Choice Products presents the new Wicker Bar Cart! Take your parties outdoors with this roll-away bar cart. This beautiful multi-brown wicker cart features a sturdy frame and table top for food preparation and serving. The cart moves on 4 wheels with a break mechanism attached for maximum safety and easy mobility. Its all-weather wicker material helps protect from moisture, mold, mildew, sun damage, and the environmental elements while outdoors. It comes equipped with a discreet storage drawer and multiple shelves for storing your favorite drinks and dishes. Your party guests will love the convenience of the Wicker Bar Cart by Best Choice Products! SPECIFICATIONS: Overall Dimensions: 39.5i"(L) x 18"(W) x 36.25"(H); Middle Shelf: 29.5i"(L) x 16.25i"(W) x 8.5i"(H); Bottom Drawer: 28.5i x 16.5i"(W) x 8.5i"(H); Table Top Dimensions: 32i"(L) x 18i"(W); Weight Capacity: 88 lbs.; Weight: 29 lbs.; Color: Brown; Material: Wicker, Steel; Assembly required (with instructions);

BCP SKU: SKY3373


Note: Take precaution during inclement weather conditions. The frame is weather-resistant, while the cushions are not. Cushion covers (not the cushion itself) are water-resistant and can withstand hand-washing or light rain. They are not waterproof.
